{"type":"message","id":"95c8840b","parentId":"b14dfb0c","timestamp":"2026-04-28T09:04:49.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gmail has no new emails in the last hour. iCloud has some emails but they're all from before the last hour (April 27 and earlier). Let me check the himalaya emails more carefully - they seem to be older emails marked as read (R flag).\n\nLet me check if there are any unread emails in iCloud from the last hour specifically.\n\nActually, looking at the timestamps:\n- ID 9: 2026-04-27 19:06+00:00 (April 27, 7:06 PM UTC = April 27, 3:06 PM EDT - this is more than 1 hour ago from 9:04 AM EDT)\n\n\n- The rest are from even earlier dates\n\nSo both accounts show no new emails from the past hour. I should report back that Gmail is clear with no new messages in the last hour, and iCloud only has older read messages from April 27 and earlier.","thinkingSignature":"6b213a355e86d215cbd1d1a8d8da627880e29b69b31c7fc9e0d00f0cfcebb5c4"},{"type":"text","text":"No new emails in the last hour from either account.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zbjmsvqld3uv_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"telegram","target":"8212808444","message":"📬 GMAIL — No new emails"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":974,"output":271,"cacheRead":19036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20281,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777367080108,"responseId":"063fab28318353aeea2f5e78e544aef6"}}
